{"tid":99080,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"林柏特盛讚三大對手：謝拉特是英超最強！","createTime":"2017-01-29T02:34:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-29T09:29:28.000Z","uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5b2aeee556c24b9b71b12407e12d8978b85d6868","tid":99080,"uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T02:34:34.000Z","msg":"不久前，前車路士中場林柏特於訪問中，盛讚前國家隊隊友「神奇隊長」謝拉特。他認為，該名現職利物浦青訓教練的英格蘭傳奇中場，是自己於英超遇過最難應付的對手。<br />\n<br />\n林柏特說：「謝拉特於國內的聯賽幾乎是無所不能，他能夠為你帶來難以應付的防守，亦可以帶領球隊全力進攻，全能性極強。」"},{"pid":"04bf0410c9d6b48a4667b1bf39d64d0a51785fd0","tid":99080,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T02:36:17.000Z","msg":"他能夠為你帶來難以應付的防守<br />\n<br />\n同意"},{"pid":"f0d504f1af48cba7100b17de77f77e8a4a68e8cd","tid":99080,"uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T02:46:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>他能夠為你帶來難以應付的防守<br />\n<br />\n同意</blockquote><br />\n同意"},{"pid":"8e405fb8fd0654b50f7c2eaefbeb0cd9676a6ec2","tid":99080,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T03:03:36.000Z","msg":"他能夠為隊友帶來難以應付的防守"},{"pid":"f7365ad540667844cde7de07d4e94744a4c625e0","tid":99080,"uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T03:15:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>他能夠為隊友帶來難以應付的防守</blockquote><br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"748a084a50143a9764b7e1fc0fbf4a4511b739bc","tid":99080,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T04:19:29.000Z","msg":"樓主好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3f930c51fddd29cf13db6fee650ad11b37f6f4","tid":99080,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T04:25:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>他能夠為你帶來難以應付的防守<br />\n<br />\n同意</blockquote><br />\n同意</blockquote><br />\n同意"},{"pid":"822273bcb34e97bc43bd36bae49f637cd61762fb","tid":99080,"uid":27701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T07:16:40.